      "span_text": "While several studies showed an increased risk of thyroid cancer linked to a family history of this cancer, the nature of the relationship between thyroid cancer and a family history of other cancers is not clear. [CITATION_1] We found five cases with a family history of thyroid cancer compared to none of the controls, but the difference was of borderline significance.",
